https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jSbEAsDbnd5LFudrs26xX5v7FY8.jpg He’s back! Stand-up comedian, best-selling author and chat show supremo, the lovable Chatty Man and Tooth Fairy himself….. Alan Carr is back on tour in autumn 2011 with a brand new live comedy show, Spexy Beast, that will also be filmed live for DVD. After a few years of rubbing shoulders with A-list celebrities on his very own chat show, award-winning Alan Carr returns to his stand-up roots in his first major comedy tour and Live DVD in four years.
